MetaTile: GoCardless Integration | Billing Cycle Automation | Cyclr
MetaDescription: Let your users integrate your application with GoCardless to help streamline their business processes
Content:
GoCardless offer a comprehensive platform for collecting recurring payments, ideal for businesses with subscription revenue models such as SaaS providers, eLearning courses, utilities and media service amongst others.

With Cyclr you can create and publish automation workflows between your app and GoCardless that will help your users automate processes such as invoice generation, CRM updating, data integrity management and much more.
